Put an ice cube in it.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.000
Yes, now squeeze.

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:24.079
That hand, squeeze it.

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:25.079
Count for yourself.

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:26.800
See how long you can last.

00:02:27.079 --> 00:02:27.520
One,

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.120
two,

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:31.000
three.

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:32.040
Tell yourself,

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:33.160
I'm not afraid,

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:34.960
it's not cold.

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:37.000
Say it.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.680
Say I'm not afraid of the cold.

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:46.560
Why are you so useless?

00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:50.160
Pick it up.

00:02:51.079 --> 00:02:51.600
Hurry.

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:54.400
Hurry up.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.160
Be good, pick it up.

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:00.440
That ice cube.

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:04.760
Can't even do this one little thing.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:08.840
Hold it,

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:09.600
you hear me?

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.280
No whining.

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:14.000
One,

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:16.120
two.

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:17.280
In your head,

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:18.360
say "I'm not afraid of the cold."

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:20.160
Say it: I'm not afraid of the cold.

00:03:22.079 --> 00:03:23.120
Say it.

