Your leg

00:17:36.520 --> 00:17:37.480
seems badly hurt...

00:17:37.480 --> 00:17:38.040
It's fine.

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:39.240
It's nothing.

00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:41.280
We'll head out.

