I just want

00:38:02.840 --> 00:38:04.640
you and dad to have your own life,

00:38:04.840 --> 00:38:05.320
and stop

00:38:05.720 --> 00:38:06.560
devoting yourselves

00:38:07.360 --> 00:38:08.760
to me every day.

