Yeah, I did it.

00:38:41.640 --> 00:38:42.760
It's because I want you

00:38:42.760 --> 00:38:44.800
to have a good life,

00:38:44.800 --> 00:38:46.720
not to stay at other people's houses.

00:38:46.720 --> 00:38:47.240
Mom,

00:38:47.520 --> 00:38:50.320
please stop running around for me.

00:38:50.320 --> 00:38:51.600
Stop obsessing over

00:38:51.600 --> 00:38:53.000
this Canada thing.

00:38:53.000 --> 00:38:55.120
Let's just breathe for once.

00:38:55.760 --> 00:38:57.160
Stop struggling

00:38:57.160 --> 00:38:58.040
in that thing.

00:38:58.720 --> 00:38:59.640
Okay, mom?

00:39:12.120 --> 00:39:13.080
How could you have

00:39:13.080 --> 00:39:14.120
the guts to do this?

