Did you say even one word to me?

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:22.040
We sold the old house,

00:39:22.200 --> 00:39:23.120
bought this one,

00:39:23.760 --> 00:39:25.320
and put it in your name.

00:39:26.040 --> 00:39:27.720
But literally this house

00:39:27.720 --> 00:39:29.880
is years of our hard work.

00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:34.160
Again and again,

00:39:34.760 --> 00:39:36.040
you hide everything

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:38.200
from me!

