What do you want to do?

00:39:47.160 --> 00:39:48.560
Tell me!

00:39:48.560 --> 00:39:50.840
You just wanna live it up all day!

00:39:50.840 --> 00:39:52.600
Never!

00:39:53.640 --> 00:39:54.520
All I want

00:39:54.520 --> 00:39:55.880
is to live my own life!

