Let me ask you...

00:39:56.920 --> 00:39:58.200
Your own life?

00:39:58.560 --> 00:39:59.920
What kind of life?

00:39:59.920 --> 00:40:01.720
I don't want to be

00:40:01.720 --> 00:40:03.480
- on top like you!
- Can you ever live

00:40:03.480 --> 00:40:05.080
with self-respect on your own?

00:40:05.480 --> 00:40:06.520
I just don't want

00:40:06.520 --> 00:40:08.600
the life you planned for me, okay?!

00:40:08.600 --> 00:40:10.400
So I am wrong to

00:40:10.400 --> 00:40:12.520
plan your life, huh?

00:40:12.520 --> 00:40:14.200
Then am I wrong

00:40:14.200 --> 00:40:15.520
to live my own life?

00:40:15.520 --> 00:40:17.080
Ever since I was little,

00:40:17.080 --> 00:40:19.120
I've just been following the path

00:40:19.120 --> 00:40:19.840
you laid out for me.

00:40:19.840 --> 00:40:20.720
Piano lessons,

00:40:20.720 --> 00:40:21.840
and Canada...

00:40:21.840 --> 00:40:23.320
Did you ever ask me

00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:24.640
whether I like this?

00:40:24.640 --> 00:40:26.040
Listen, Lu Xinying.

00:40:27.240 --> 00:40:27.880
You'll

00:40:27.880 --> 00:40:29.280
be a mother one day.

