What does it mean to be a parent?

00:40:32.880 --> 00:40:34.320
What do you like?

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:37.840
Tell me, what do you like?

00:40:38.560 --> 00:40:40.240
Kids like to eat,

00:40:40.240 --> 00:40:41.200
drink,

00:40:41.200 --> 00:40:42.200
sleep,

00:40:42.200 --> 00:40:43.160
and have fun.

00:40:44.040 --> 00:40:44.920
What if they grow up?

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:47.400
What if you're

00:40:47.400 --> 00:40:48.960
middle-aged?

